textAnnotation.text: Assumption: the applicant should verify his registration on the government website in order to successfully apply for jobs
Assumption: A job application can not be executed until the applicant is registered
Assumption: if the applicant is not interested in a job offer then he/she should research new job advertisements
Additional info: Reviews for a company is visible for job applicants after 1 year
